.TH erasechar 3
.SH NAME
\*Lerasechar\*O \- Returns the current ERASE character
.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
.sS
\*L#include <curses.h>\*O

\*Lchar erasechar(\|)\*O
.sE
.SH DESCRIPTION
.iX "erasechar subroutine"
.PP
The user's current erase character is returned.
.SH RETURN VALUES
.PP
The \*Lerasechar\*O
function returns the user's current erase character.
.EQ
